MNTD/
├─ README.md
├─ requirements.txt
├─ config.yaml
├─ src/
│  ├─ __init__.py
│  ├─ preprocess.py        # load CSVs, min-max scaling, one-hot, channel construction
│  ├─ model.py             # MNTD model (Conv1D, BiLSTM with ELU, MHA, FC)
│  ├─ losses.py            # adaptive loss, contrastive loss
│  ├─ awdv.py              # simplified PSO-AWDV hyperparameter tuner
│  ├─ sampling.py          # triplet sampling and batch builder
│  ├─ train.py             # training loop (includes AWDV hook)
│  └─ eval.py              # evaluation metrics, confusion matrix, ROC curves
└─ scripts/
   └─ run_train.sh
